ethirtyeight\">{{Cite web|url=https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/polls/kentucky/|title=Kentucky Polls|website=fivethirtyeight.com}}</ref>\n| Jan 17-21, 2020\n| 1281\n| \u00b1&nbsp;2.8%\n| '''41%'''\n| '''41%'''\n| 11%\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| Garin-Hart-Yang <ref name=\"fivethirtyeight\"/>\n| Jan 8-13, 2020\n| 802\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.5%\n| {{party shading/Republican}}| '''43%'''\n| 40%\n| 12%\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.aarp.org/content/dam/aarp/research/surveys_statistics/politics/2019/five-state-prescription-drug-survey-annotated-questionnaire-KY.doi.10.26419-2Fres.00335.003.pdf Fabrizio Ward/AARP]\n| July 29\u201331, 2019\n| 600\n| \u00b1&nbsp;4.0%\n| {{party shading/Republican}}| '''47%'''\n| 46%\n| 5%\n|}\n\n{{collapse top|1=<span style=\"font-size:88%;\">Hypothetical polling</span>|left=yes|bg=#B0CEFF;line-height:135%;|border=none}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|Key:<br>A \u2013 all adults<br>RV \u2013 registered voters<br>LV \u2013 likely voters<br>V \u2013 unclear}}\n! Margin<br>of error\n! style=\"width:100px;\"| Mitch<br>McConnell (R)\n! style=\"width:100px;\"| Generic<br>Democrat\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://ditchmitchfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/KentuckyMemoFeb21.pdf Public Policy Polling (D)]{{efn-ua|Poll sponsored by The Ditch Mitch Fund|name=\"TMDF\"}}\n| Feb 11\u201312, 2019\n| 748\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.6%\n| {{party shading/Republican}}| '''45%'''\n| 42%\n| 12%\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|Key:<br>A \u2013 all adults<br>RV \u2013 registered voters<br>LV \u2013 likely voters<br>V \u2013 unclear}}\n! Margin<br>of error\n! style=\"width:100px;\"| Mitch<br>McConnell (R)\n! style=\"width:100px;\"| Jim<br>Gray (D)\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align: